title: Mozart Premium Edition (40CDs) MP3 128Kb
description:
Ripped from the Amado Classics 40CD collection of Mozart music, includes the majority of Mozart&#039;s well known pieces, such as Eine Kliene Nachtmusik (A Little Night Music), excerpts from The Magic Flute, and the Requiem.  Below is a partial list of orchestras, conductors, and soloists (from the box the CDs came in).
